dc_title_s: Kaisei Yokohama bunken chizu: zen; Ozaki Tomigorō.; Yokohama bunken chizu
dc_description_s: Wood block print. Oriented with north to the lower right. Relief shown pictorially. Includes inset map of horse-race track. Includes legend and lists of town names, bridges, railway schedules and fares, distance charts, flags of foreign nations, etc. 1 map: col.; 35 x 62 m., folded to 13 x 9 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
